## Catalog rule

`catalog/` holds document types, parse/serialize, and manifest data ‚Äî **no registry writes, no spawn logic**.

| Belongs in `catalog/` | Belongs outside `catalog/` |
|-----------------------|----------------------------|
| `PropDocument` / `ActorDocument` / `LevelDocument` types + parse/serialize | `spawnPropEditor`, `spawnActorEditor`, `spawnLevelEditor` |
| `CONSTRUCT_KEYS` component key strings | `install*System` |
| `KaykitManifest` types, `loadKaykitManifest`, tree filters | `bootstrap` composition |
| Document ‚Üî `PropDefinition`/`ActorDefinition`/`LevelDefinition` converters | Session slices (`session/*`) |
| `slugifyDocumentId` | UI hooks, React components |

**`catalog/` must not import from `entities/`, `session/`, `scenes/`, `globals/`, or `ui/`.**

## Level mode UI (summary)

- Explorer: unified tree with **Simple** (props/actors from manifest), **Standard** (local `.prop`/`.actor`), and **Colliders**; bottom **Import** for `.prop`/`.actor`. `+` places at orbit target.
- Elements: Level ‚Üí Ground Plane ‚Üí Player Spawn ‚Üí Props/Actors (Simple|Standard when non-empty) ‚Üí Colliders ‚Üí Groups. Empty subgroups hidden. Ctrl multi-select; group select selects members.
- Details: rename; simple variants; actor `aiPackage`; Group / Delete footer; ground plane and player spawn non-deletable (ground: move+scale only; player spawn: move+yaw only).
- Actor tool Animations (actor root): Hit / Death / Death pose clip names from `animPack.generalGlb` (defaults `hit_a`, `death_a`, `death_a_pose` ‚Üí Kaykit `Hit_A` / `Death_A` / `Death_A_Pose`).
- Preview HUD: status + Show colliders (prop/actor/level); Show bones (actor only).
- Gizmos: instance / group root / temp multi-select pivot; world move; TRS relative to level origin; scale collider-only or ground plane; actors/player spawn yaw-only rotate; ground plane no rotate.
- Rotated box colliders (prop parts or level collider placements) serve as **ramps** at runtime ‚Äî no dedicated ramp type; slope walk/slide behavior is angle-based in the CPU collision resolver.
- Files: `.level` save/load/import/export via `levelLocalStore` (`construct.levelLocalStore`).

## Entity rule

| Folder | Role |
|--------|------|
| `entities/editorCommon/` | Shared mechanics: origin marker, collider shape resources, `editableTarget`, `editorSelection`, materials, TRS, `syncPartLocal` |
| `entities/actorEditor/` | Actor root/character/attachment/collider components + `spawnActor*` + `installActorColliderFollowSystem` |
| `entities/propEditor/` | Prop root/part components + `spawnAssetPart`/`spawnColliderPart`/`spawnPropEditor` |
| `entities/levelEditor/` | Level root/origin, placement spawns, selection pivots, viewport pick helpers |
| `entities/gizmos/` | Move/scale/rotate gizmo meshes, picking, input, `installConstructGizmoSystem` |
| `entities/orbit/` | Orbit camera state, origin marker, anim preview entity, `installConstructOrbitSystem` |

Shared editor mechanics live in `entities/editorCommon/` ‚Äî never duplicate origin marker, collider, or TRS logic per-editor.

## Session rule

- `session/types.ts` ‚Äî `ConstructSession`, `ConstructSessionState`, `ConstructSessionDeps` types + `createConstructSessionState`
- `session/preview.ts` ‚Äî standalone asset preview load/texture-variant slice
- `session/propEditor.ts` ‚Äî prop document mutation slice
- `session/actorEditor.ts` ‚Äî actor document mutation slice
- `session/levelEditor.ts` ‚Äî level document mutation slice (placements, groups, gizmo commit)
- `session/anim.ts` ‚Äî animation pack load/apply/clear slice

Session slices are pure functions of `(deps, state, ...)` returning updated documents ‚Äî no React, no JSX. System installers live in `scenes/installEditorSystems.ts`.

## Globals rule

`globals/bootstrap.ts` composes engine primitives into a `ConstructSession` ‚Äî composition only, no document mutation logic.

## Storage rule

- `storage/localStore.ts` ‚Äî generic `createLocalStore<TDoc>(storageKey)` factory
- `storage/actorLocalStore.ts` / `storage/propLocalStore.ts` / `storage/levelLocalStore.ts` ‚Äî thin wrappers

Do not reimplement read/write/list/remove localStorage logic per document type ‚Äî extend `localStore.ts`.

## UI rule

- `ui/app/ConstructApp.tsx` ‚Äî layout shell only; delegates to `useConstruct*.ts` hooks
- UI talks only to `ConstructSession` or catalog helpers ‚Äî **never import `entities/` from `ui/`**
- `ui/inspector/shared.tsx` ‚Äî shared details helpers

## Forbidden

- Barrel `index.ts` anywhere under `construct/src/`
- Comments in agent-generated `.ts`/`.tsx` source
- God objects in `globals/bootstrap.ts` or `ui/app/ConstructApp.tsx`
- Component key strings outside `catalog/keys/components.ts`
- Duplicated inspector helpers ‚Äî use `ui/inspector/shared.tsx`
- Duplicated localStorage logic ‚Äî use `storage/localStore.ts`
- `entities/` imports from `ui/`
- Editing embedded standard prop/actor internals from level mode
